A powerfully-modern tool for writing, drawing, note-taking, and beyond.
L'outil qui runit vos croquis, diagrammes et notes

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Ingeniously designed, Paper presents a powerfully modern tool for writing, drawing, note-taking, and beyond. Sketch out ideas and whip up diagrams with a rich selection of responsive brushes. Using simple gestures, quickly annotate photos or transform text into beautifully formatted lists. Its an excellent medium for capturing and organizing the thoughts and images that you need every day.

Ingeniously designed, Paper presents a powerfully modern tool for writing, drawing, note-taking and beyond. Sketch out ideas and whip up diagrams with a rich selection of responsive brushes. Using simple gestures, quickly annotate photos or transform text into beautifully formatted lists. Its an excellent medium for capturing and organising the thoughts and images that you need every day.

Textes, dessins, prise de notes et plus encore : Paper est un outil  la fois puissant et intuitif qui vous permet de mettre en page toutes vos ides en esquisses et diagrammes de toutes sortes. En quelques gestes simples, vous pouvez facilement annoter des photos, convertir votre texte en listes et organiser vos images et penses du quotidien.
